<lb n="0847b26"/><p>曩謨&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>倪也<note place="inline">二合</note>波<note place="inline">引</note>囉彌多<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0847007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曳＝曳引【三】【宮】</note><note n="0847007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曳＝曳引【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0847007"><lem>曳</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">曳引</rdg></app>怛&CB00135;也
<lb n="0847b27"/><note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;帝&CB00344;帝波<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00772;&CB00344;帝波<note place="inline">引</note>帝囉僧&CB00344;帝
<lb n="0847b28"/>冒地娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0847008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＝賀引【明】</note><app n="0847008"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0847b29"/><p>爾時世尊說此經已。帝釋天主。及諸菩薩摩
<pb ed="T" id="T08.0249.0847c" n="0847c"/>
<lb n="0847c01"/>訶薩。天人乾闥婆阿修羅等。一切大眾。聞佛
<lb n="0847c02"/>所說皆大歡喜。信受奉行</p>
